<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">

<head>
  <% include partials/head %>
  <title>Contact Support - Game Store</title>
</head>

<body>
  <% include partials/menu %>

  <main class="contact-content">
    <h1>Hubungi Layanan Pelanggan Game Store</h1>
    <p>Jika Anda memiliki pertanyaan, membutuhkan bantuan, atau ingin memberikan umpan balik, tim layanan pelanggan kami siap membantu Anda.</p>

    <section class="contact-details">
      <h2>Informasi Kontak</h2>
      <p>Anda dapat menghubungi kami melalui beberapa cara berikut:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Telepon:</strong> 0-800-123-4567 (Senin - Sabtu, 08.00 - 18.00)</li>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@gamestore.com">support@gamestore.com</a></li>
        <li><strong>Alamat:</strong> Jl. Gaming Center No. 42, Jakarta, Indonesia</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="contact-form">
      <h2>Kirim Pesan kepada Kami</h2>
      <form action="/contact" method="POST">
        <label for="name">Nama:</label>
        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>

        <label for="email">Email:</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>

        <label for="subject">Subjek:</label>
        <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" required>

        <label for="message">Pesan:</label>
        <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>

        <button type="submit">Kirim Pesan</button>
      </form>
    </section>

    <section class="social-media">
      <h2>Ikuti Kami di Media Sosial</h2>
      <p>Dapatkan informasi terbaru, promo, dan update game melalui akun media sosial kami:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://facebook.com/gamestore" target="_blank">Facebook</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://twitter.com/gamestore" target="_blank">Twitter</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://instagram.com/gamestore" target="_blank">Instagram</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>Â© 2024 Game Store. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

  <% include partials/script %>

</body>

</html>
